  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  ASA class II or III

          -  Mild to moderate obstructive or restrictive lung disease

          -  Open nephrectomy candidate patients

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Any condition contra-indicating regional anesthesia

          -  Allergic to any of the drugs used during the procedure
      </textblock>
    </criteria>
